txt.en: 'Tol Ascarnen is fallen! Across the river, now! We shall return to claim it another day!'
'Smash the foe! Hold nothing at reserve, arise and slay the fiends! Arise and drive back the dark! Arise!'
'These halls may be halls of Men, but the walls are sturdy and this Dwarf is not so daft as to leave them!'
'Let us see this through to conclusion, I promise I will spill your blood on this ground!'
'Strength and honour! Strike these foes and bring them down!'
'Angmar arrives! To the defence of Tol Ascarnen! Come all, drive them back!'
